### Example 01: Basic Routes
### Server: http://localhost:3000

### Ping - Simple string return
GET http://localhost:3000/ping

### List Users - Auto JSON response
GET http://localhost:3000/users

### Create User - Request binding with validation
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Charlie",
  "email": "charlie@example.com"
}

### Create User - Validation error (missing email)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dave"
}

### Create User - Validation error (invalid email)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Eve",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}
